# Web Language Translator

A web-based language translation application that supports
text-to-text/speech and audio-to-audio/text translation between multiple languages.

## Features
- Text translation between English, Hindi, Marathi
- Audio input and output translation
- Real-time speech processing
- User-friendly web interface

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Flask
- gtts
- AssemblyAI API
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript

## Live Demo
https://weblanguagetranslator-1.onrender.com

## How to Run
1. Clone the repo
2. Install dependencies
3. Set environment variables
4. Run app.py
